.TH ALLOCB 9
.SH NAME
allocb, iallocb, freeb, freeblist, BLEN, blocklen, concatblock, copyblock, trimblock, packblock, padblock, pullblock, pullupblock, adjustblock, checkb \- data block management
.SH SYNOPSIS
.ta \w'\fLBlock* 'u
